            "subheading": "",
            "title": "promise keepsake card",
            "content": "<p>Every ring purchase comes with a complimentary keepsake card - <strong>a little piece of your journey.</strong></p><p>This card is more than just a token;<strong> </strong>it's a canvas for your most cherished promises.</p>",
